high_descs: Pick up cup from sink, second cup on the right.
Turn around, go to wall, turn left.  Proceed to refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, place cup on top shelf left of tomato.  Shut refrigerator, wait four seconds, open refrigerator.  Remove cup, shut refrigerator.
Place cup on table in front of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Get cup from sink, chill in refrigerator, put cup on table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the rightmost cup in the sink.
Turn around and veer left to the fridge.
Place the cup in the fridge on the same shelf and to the left of the apple. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and walk to the table in front of you.
Place the cup on the table in front of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled cup on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and then right to move to the sink.
Pick up the clear cup from the right side of the sink.
Hold the cup and turn around. Then turn left and face the fridge.
Open the door and place the cup inside. Shut the door and then open it. Take out the cup and shut the door.
Hold the cup and turn around to move to the brown table.
Place the cup on the front edge of the brown table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and place it on the table.
